      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Stance)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 0</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>While in this stance, each time an adjacent opponent misses you with a melee attack, you may make an at- tack of opportunity as an instant action costing 6 Chakra. You gain a +2 bonus to the attack roll for such attacks.</p>\n\n\n\n",
